{"tid":759702,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"怎樣叫兔仔回到籠裡？不要抱！","createTime":"2018-07-29T01:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T01:10:38.000Z","uid":197098,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"52e7ddd9703ffa0d96b0ca424d64ef5ce3455851","tid":759702,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T01:10:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兔子是被捕獵的動物(prey animal), 在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predatory animals)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚。因此，兔子不喜歡被抱來抱去。當牠逃跑的時候，你還去追住抱，會令兔子和主人的信任更差。最好的方法去叫牠入籠是每晚(比如：22:00）搖零食樽或pellet 樽幾下，再引牠進入籠吃。幾天後，兔子就會記得零食樽的聲音知道是時候回到籠吃。習慣後，牠會自動22:00左右提主人你是時候回到籠裡吃東西。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">以下video 有教：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RJcvi7o4YXA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRJcvi7o4YXA&d=EiDfJdQdG%2FZi7HAVwIfDtEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=53aa651f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RJcvi7o4YXA</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更多關於兔子的身體語言(開心、憂愁、憤怒、驚慌)： <a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=EiDfJdQdG%2FZi7HAVwIfDtEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c8b21fd6\" target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a></span>"}]}